{"tid":1567690,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我地係咪已經放棄左連儂牆戰術？","createTime":"2019-09-14T06:55:07.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T06:58:22.000Z","uid":317651,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"bd789691ae98c6ea4d6e25f9a31a71522d9d28fe","tid":1567690,"uid":317651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:55:07.000Z","msg":"六七月都見到仲有後生會痴連儂牆<br />\n而家得翻中老年守牆<br />\n香港人可唔可以唔好再三分鐘熱度<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以 我正式宣布<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">連登第一屆連儂牆打卡大賽</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">正式開始</span> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n現諴繳各巴絲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係今個星期五六日<br />\n去盡港九新界十八區連儂牆<br />\n痴文宣/或memo<br />\n完成後打一個靚卡comment<br />\n務求擴大連儂牆嘅各種文宣形式<br />\n勝出者可獲得<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">「連儂之王」</span></span>稱號<br />\n歡迎踴躍參加<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e9606fa086548b65ee1d37ea88960e2c3486eaef","tid":1567690,"uid":317651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:55:44.000Z","msg":"p牌仔求幫推"},{"pid":"2674df439a9c0d9f7ed5f2411d5df5b0b9282dde","tid":1567690,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T06:57:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日見！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktW8Y1Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktW8Y1Q.jpg&h=d39b859f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/1veB7Va.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih